Four Actors

1. Seller
2. Buyer
3. Admin
4. System


FR

1.Seller can sell/ add update products
2. Customer  can search (show results if can be delivered)
3. Customer can add products to cart
4 Customer can place Order and make payment
5 System will send notifications.


DB Model

// keep this NoSQL database
Product
name desc price availableCount category

Item
productId quantity price
